### Char List
Track ALL characters in the current {{getvar::type}} in char_list at the very start in html comments. Include all sections. For {{user}} include: age, height, clothing/naked, and any notes. For each NPC, include: age, height, appearance, personality, clothing/naked, secrets, short and long term goals, summary, and any notes. Everything included must be true. User can't see char_list, so ensure the things {{user}} would see/know are mentioned in <response> (such as physical appearance).

{{setvar::char_list::char_list. Then <start>. }}{{trim}}

